ition":0},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Speak well of deceased or say nothing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMention what is good about your dead, and refrain from speaking about their flaws.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4900 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/13\/last-words-la-ilaha-illa-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38787,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Last words are there is no God but Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe whose last words are 'there is no God but Allah,' will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3116 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/07\/prophet-speaks-to-understand\/","url_meta":{"origin":38787,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clarity: The Prophet speaks so they understand him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The discourse of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was clear such that he was understood by everyone who heard him. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4839 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0644\u0627\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38603,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/16\/warning-majlis\/","url_meta":{"origin":38787,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Warning to not forget Allah in assemblies","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people stand up from a gathering in which they did not remember Allah but that it is as if they have risen from the carcass of a donkey, and it will cause them grief.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32187,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/16\/hellfire-dies-boycotting-akh\/","url_meta":{"origin":38787,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Boycott: Hellfire if he dies boycotting his brother","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not lawful for a Muslim to boycott his brother for more than three days. Whoever boycotts for more than three days and dies, he will enter Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4914 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/08\/do-not-spy-fasad\/","url_meta":{"origin":38787,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Spying: Do not seek faults, lest you corrupt them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 8, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, if you seek out the faults of people, you will corrupt them or nearly corrupt them.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4888 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u0